description:
Robert Greene is a New York Times Best Selling author of 6 powerful books on human psychology. 
 
The 48 Laws of Power, The Art Of Seduction, Mastery, The 33 Strategies Of War, The 50th Law, and The Laws Of Human Nature will leave you mind blown.
 
In this episode, you’ll learn how to use your underdog mentality to maximum effect, and so much more.
 
If I could be personally mentored by ANYONE in the world, I would choose Robert Greene. His understanding of human nature is mind boggling.
